WorldPositionOriginType: Defines the reference space for the Position input.
NoiseFunction: Noise function, affects performance and look
Quality: For noise functions where applicable, lower numbers are faster and lower quality, higher numbers are slower and higher quality
TileSize:
How many units in each tile (if Tiling is on)
For Perlin noise functions, Tile Size must be a multiple of three
bTiling: Whether tile the noise pattern, useful for baking to seam-free repeating textures
